name: ShelS Company
tag_list: gis, map, mapdraw, mapserver, transform, land, estimate, develop, service, geodetic
overview:
SHELS Company is the developer of software for GIS, mapping and cadaster, registration of rights to land and real estate. The company has introduced in the Ukraine a lot of networking solutions with a unified system of databases and cartographic material. The latest developments allow the company to build web based solutions using geo-spatial data.

SHELS company was founded in 2008, but the beginning of the creation of the systems and technology was launched in September 1997.

Currently, the Company Shels distribute any ready-made solutions in the field of GIS technology and registration systems, as well as carrying out professional development and support of innovative software products and services. Thousands of people use to work posvednevnoy Software Products developed by the company.

The professional team allows the company to perform in the shortest time to develop or adapt existing development to the needs of the customer. We are always looking for ways to improve the solutions to meet the needs of our clients.
